item.title: About: Emma Jane Hogbin
item.description: Hi! I’m an expat Canadian living and working in Yeovil, UK. During the day I manage the Web operations team for the Digital Services team at the Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs at the United Nations. Previously, I’ve worked for Phase2, and Lullabot. I’ve taught Web technologies at both Seneca Collegeand Humber College, as well as knitting, crochet, and bookbinding classes at various shops in Canada. I have delivered presentations at conferences across North America, Europe, and New Zealand.
